====================== Information for New Users =========================

POD is a PODnuts chat program (by Crandonkphin and Vaghn), based around 
rnuts (by Engi and Slugger), which itself is based around nuts (by Neil
Robertson).

It is here for one and all as a place for dolphin lovers to just relax 
and chat.

Look around and enjoy yourself. If you find that you like it and would 
like a Permanent Account, then just ask one of our Adphins for 
"Residency" by using the .accreq command. If you need information on 
how to use POD, just type ".help" once you are online.

If you have any problems then email the adphins at pod@ncohafmuta.com

===========================================================================
